"```sql\nSELECT \n    (COUNT(*) * 100.0 / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM event)) AS percentage_over_budget\nFROM \n    budget\nWHERE \n    remaining < 0;\n```\n\nThis SQL query calculates the percentage of events that went over budget by counting the number of budget entries where the remaining amount is less than zero and dividing it by the total number of events, then multiplying by 100 to get the percentage."